abstract: A NASA official says that a fighter jet owned by Google executives will be used mostly to fly missions that their four other jets could not handle.
snippet: A NASA official says that a fighter jet owned by Google executives will be used mostly to fly missions that their four other jets could not handle.
lead_paragraph: A NASA official said Friday that the top Googlers’ new fighter jet will be used mostly to fly missions for the agency that four other jets owned by Google’s top executives could not handle.

headline.main: Google Founders’ Fighter Jet Will Fly NASA Missions
